<HL>
   Best Buy April Sales Up
</HL>
<DATE>
05/10/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   BBY
</CO>
<LP>
   MINNEAPOLIS -- Best Buy Co. said its April sales rose 20%
to $36 million from $30 million a year earlier.
   The retailer of consumer electronic goods and major
appliances said year-to-date sales for the nine weeks were up
19% to $87 million from $73 million in the year-ago period.
